# Public package/object IDs only. Rill Cloud never accepts a signing key.
# ONE agent_wallet package: the redesigned Rule + Hot Potato + version gate design (scope rules
# off-chain), deployed and rehearsed live on testnet. Every agent wallet binding compiles the
# request_spend -> prove x N -> confirm_spend sequence against THIS package + AGENT_WALLET_VERSION_ID
# — see `core/agent-wallet.ts`'s `normalizeAgentWallet`. A wallet bound without a capabilityManifest
# is rejected (422); there is no legacy manifest-less spend() package/path anymore.
AGENT_WALLET_PACKAGE_ID=0xb02f39d682d0471344b1cc264f6f29d625280b9e73560d5beee3db3090563740
